704337f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Johnson Street
704337f-a.text:
Flatbush Ave. Extension, west side, north from Johnson Street. Also seen is Johnson Street, north side, west from Flatbush Ave. Extension.
July 1, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
